# Walkthrough: Residency+ Production Restoration

Successfully restored the Residency+ production environment after resolving critical 502 errors and frontend initialization failures.

## Resolved Issues

### 1. Production 502 (Backend)
- **Root Cause**: Netlify Functions V2 ESM/CJS incompatibility and shared library bundling errors.
- **Resolution**: Refactored all backend functions to CommonJS and relocated [sc-auth-lib.js](file:///c:/Users/sean/antigravity-awesome-skills/prototypes/residency-plus/netlify/functions/sc-auth-lib.js) to `netlify/functions/lib/`.
- **Validation**: [verify_prod.ps1](file:///c:/Users/sean/antigravity-awesome-skills/prototypes/residency-plus/scripts/verify_prod.ps1) passed with 100% success rate on all endpoints.

### 2. Fatal Frontend Initialization
- **Root Cause**: Significant code duplication in [index.html](file:///c:/Users/sean/antigravity-awesome-skills/prototypes/residency-plus/index.html) causing a fatal `SyntaxError`.
- **Resolution**: Surgically excised redundant logic and restored over-aggressive cleanup items ([normalizeUrl](file:///c:/Users/sean/antigravity-awesome-skills/prototypes/residency-plus/index.html#1321-1329), [sleep](file:///c:/Users/sean/antigravity-awesome-skills/prototypes/residency-plus/index.html#1206-1208), [setProgress](file:///c:/Users/sean/antigravity-awesome-skills/prototypes/residency-plus/index.html#1402-1403)).
- **Optimization**: Refactored [scSearch](file:///c:/Users/sean/antigravity-awesome-skills/prototypes/residency-plus/index.html#1431-1454) for pooled requests to prevent initialization hangs.

### 3. Playback Synchronization
- **Root Cause**: Missing global declaration for `scWidget` and lack of a surgical fallback for the SoundCloud API.
- **Resolution**: Surgery-declared `scWidget`, implemented a robust `w.load` with a structural `src` reload fallback, and updated [buildEmbedUrl](file:///c:/Users/sean/antigravity-awesome-skills/prototypes/residency-plus/index.html#1397-1400) to support dynamic autoplay.

